short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension provides connectivity between the browser and Blue Prism.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
INTENDED FOR ENTERPRISE USE ONLY.

This allows users of the Blue Prism software to automate and interact with websites using Google Chrome.
To use this extension, users also need Blue Prism 7.0: https://www.blueprism.com
